title: Rapacious Hunger
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

In the turn in which a [[Haruspex]] charges, every unsaved Wound that it inflicts in close combat immediately allows it to make an additional Attack. These bonus Attacks cannot generate further Attacks. Wounds that inflict [[Instant Death]] only generate one bonus Attack. Note that Wounds caused by its [[Hammer of Wrath]], [[acid blood|Acid Blood]] or tail biomorph do not benefit from this rule.